description: List all of the tags for a DAX cluster. You can call ListTags up to 10 times per second, per account.

parameters.name: ResourceName
parameters.description: The name of the DAX resource to which the tags belong.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: A list of tags currently associated with the DAX cluster.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: The key for the tag. Tag keys are case sensitive. Every DAX cluster can only have one tag with the same key. If you try to add an existing tag (same key), the existing tag value will be updated to the new value.

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: The value of the tag. Tag values are case-sensitive and can be null.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If this value is present, there are additional results to be displayed. To retrieve them, call ListTags again, with NextToken set to this value.
